title: Press Releases: Secretary Kerry To Attend Dinner in honor of Indonesian President Joko Widodo (US ...
text: ( Source : US Department of State ) U.S. Secretary of State John Kerry will deliver remarks at a dinner in honor of Indonesian President Joko Widodo hosted by the U.S. Chamber of Commerce , at 7:00 p.m. on October 26 , 2015 , at the U.S. Chamber
